{"type": "article", "id": 4492, "title": "Campbell Cole 皮革钥匙包", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-18T07:41:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233608bXWQiK3IVBdCE9Mc.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"font-size:11px;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t英国品牌 Campbell Cole 出品的东西向来都是以极简的造型取胜，在设计团队看来，简洁是生活美学中不可错过的关键词，正如这款皮革钥匙包。出门时，我们总担心随身装的钥匙有可能在手机、钱包或者其他贵重物品上刮出划痕，也许你还会颇费周折地要在包内寻觅一块单独隔开的小空间收纳钥匙，而这款包覆性较为完整的皮革钥匙包就是用来解决这一问题的，设计团队选用了意大利荤鞣皮革制成一个卷曲的包裹形状，将钥匙用钢丝绳拴于其中，避免了与包内或口袋里的其他物品产生直接接触。提供石灰色、栎棕色、黑色以及白色 4 种选择，定价 25 英镑，<a href=\"http://www.campbellcole.co.uk/products/?item=simple-key-wrap-oak\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:11px;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233606PMpaWsU0X3R2f5hT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233606u7BNKxDf2XtCr1Vi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233607w7W8FMZzChXOdmb2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233607oCwubfG1rZEJicas.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}